# Optimize Docker build context
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/README.md
**/LICENSE
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/node_modules
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/coverage
**/dist
**/build
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/tmp
**/temp
**/*.log

# Keep only what's needed for container build
!justfile
!shell/
!valeo-*.crt
!Dockerfile
